  "texts": [
    "These keywords are frequently used in the literature and are the most commonly mapped subject areas in our dataset.",
    "This finding suggests that researchers in the medical imaging field are primarily focused on addressing challenges in medical imaging through AI techniques, particularly Deep Learning and Machine Learning, to enhance the accuracy of breast cancer screening and prognosis prediction.",
    "Additionally, the keyword frequency analysis reflects a shift in research priorities on breast cancer, its diagnosis, and related imaging techniques.",
    "Terms like \"breast cancer\" (1444), \"diagnostic imaging\" (708), and \"digital mammography\" (315) emphasise the critical role of imaging in cancer detection.",
    "Artificial intelligence (1691), including deep learning (892) and convolutional neural networks (342), is increasingly used for improving diagnostic accuracy (401)."
  ]
}